    background-color: #e6f7ff;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0;
    border-radius: 5px;
    line-height: 1.6;">How do I configure asp.net core web service to use TLS 1.2 via appsettings.json configuration file</div><br/><br/>LLM response:<br/><div style="
    background-color: #fff3e6;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0;
    border-radius: 5px;
    line-height: 1.6;"><p>To configure an ASP.NET Core web service to use TLS 1.2 via the <code>appsettings.json</code> configuration file, follow these steps:</p>
<ol>
<li>
<p>Open the <code>appsettings.json</code> file in your ASP.NET Core project.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Add a new section for configuring the TLS options. For example:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><code>json
   "TlsOptions": {
     "Protocol": "Tls12"
   }</code></p>
<ol>
<li>Configure the server to use the provided TLS options. Modify the <code>ConfigureServices</code> method in the <code>Startup.cs</code> file as follows:</li>
</ol>
<p>```csharp<br />
   using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Server.Kestrel.Core;</p>
<p>public class Startup<br />
   {<br />
       // ...</p>
<pre><code>   public void ConfigureServices(IServiceCollection services)
   {
       // ...
       services.Configure&lt;KestrelServerOptions&gt;(Configuration.GetSection("TlsOptions"));
       // ...
   }

   // ...
</code></pre>
<p>}<br />
   ```</p>
<ol>
<li>Configure Kestrel to use the provided TLS options. Modify the <code>ConfigureServices</code> method in the <code>Startup.cs</code> file as follows:</li>
</ol>
<p><code>csharp
   public void Configure(IApplicationBuilder app, IWebHostEnvironment env)
   {
       // ...
       var tlsOptions = app.ApplicationServices.GetService&lt;IOptions&lt;KestrelServerOptions&gt;&gt;().Value;
       tlsOptions.ConfigureEndpointDefaults(opts =&gt; opts.Protocols = tlsOptions.Protocols | SslProtocols.Tls12);
       // ...
   }</code></p>
<ol>
<li>Build and run your ASP.NET Core web service.</li>
</ol>
<p>By following these steps, your ASP.NET Core web service will be configured to use TLS 1.2 as specified in the <code>appsettings.json</code> configuration file.</p></div>

