<p>As the memories flooded his mind, Derek – now Cassy – felt a strange sense of peace wash over him. The emptiness that had plagued him for so long was suddenly replaced by a sense of purpose and belonging. Cassy stood up from the couch, her heart brimming with gratitude for her new life.</p>
