<p>One day, as he sat on his threadbare couch, he made a fateful decision. He would change his memories, morphing himself into a completely different person. And so, with a deep breath, he willed himself to believe that he was and always had been an extremely polite and humble maid named Cassy.</p>
<p>As the memories flooded his mind, Derek – now Cassy – felt a strange sense of peace wash over him. The emptiness that had plagued him for so long was suddenly replaced by a sense of purpose and belonging. Cassy stood up from the couch, her heart brimming with gratitude for her new life.</p>
<p>However, as Cassy explored her newfound identity, a thought crept into her mind. She had always been envious of women with ample bosoms, and now that she had the power to shape herself as she pleased, she couldn't resist the temptation to indulge in this desire.</p>
<p>She retrieved a notebook from a nearby shelf, flipping through the pages until she found a hastily scrawled order to herself. With a mischievous smile, she read aloud, "I command myself to grow huge boobs, so stunning that all who lay eyes upon them are rendered speechless."</p>
<p>As she spoke the words, a warm tingling sensation spread through her chest, and before her eyes, her modest bust swelled into a luscious, voluptuous size. Cassy couldn't help but laugh in delight, marveling at the transformation she had brought upon herself.</p>
<p>"That's better," she said to herself, running her hands over her newfound curves. "Now I truly feel like the glamorous maid Cassy, ready to take on any challenge that comes her way."</p>
<p>And so, Cassy embraced her new reality, reveling in the power she held over her own existence. With a twinkle in her eye and a skip in her step, she set about transforming her apartment into a dazzling palace fit for a maid of her stature.</p>
<p>As she worked, she chattered happily to herself, her voice filling the empty rooms with warmth and cheer. "Oh, Cassy, you've truly outdone yourself this time," she exclaimed, admiring her handiwork.</p>
<p>And as the days passed, Cassy's apartment transformed into a haven of beauty and luxury, reflecting the newfound confidence and joy that now defined her life. And though she was alone in her physical form, her mind was alive with the vibrant energy of her colorful imagination, a world where anything was possible and every dream could come true. And in that world, Cassy was the queen, ruling over her domain with grace and power, a testament to the boundless potential that lay within each and every one of us.</p></div>

