    line-height: 1.6;">Planet Frenya<br/>Frenya is fascist homeworld of ahmuivns, fairly cold desert planet orbits around binary star systems, main star Zorya is yellow main sequence and close companion Vorolak is hot white dwarf, located in spiral galaxy named Euyomdu, Frenya is capital of fascist empire named Frenyan Empire. Equator is gray desert made of sands and gravels, composed of two desert materials are stones and opals. Frenya has no oceans, two hemispheres between equator and ice poles are forests and grasslands, Frenya has two large ice poles. Blue atmosphere is made of carbon monoxide, nitrogen, oxygen, neon. Plants are blue due to contains pigment phycocyanin, Frenya has two rocky moons named Iskraluna and Raznozh. Frenya as malicious civilization, signal detected by people of Aphomia galaxy.<br/>The People<br/>Ahmuivn (scientific name aviathus sanguinis) is sophont spacefaring avian species native to Frenya, one of genus aviathus, sanguinis is derived from Latin word for blood. Appearance is avian humanoid with feathered skins, head same as pigeons, two legs and two arms resemble pigeon’s leg. Ahmuivns lack wings, hands and feet resembles pigeon’s foot but have 5 fingers and toes, 10 sharp claws. Color range of eye iris between light blue and dark blue, darkness is presence of melanin, brightness is lack of melanin, high melanin eye irises are dark blue alternative to brown. They have tetrachromacy, can see four colors are red, green, blue, ultraviolet. Bloods are blue due to presence of pigment cuproglobin, iron in hemoglobin is replaced with copper, cuproglobin can binds to oxygens and carbon monoxides, term “cuproglobin” derived from prefix cupro- means copper and suffix -globin from hemoglobin. Ahmuivn skeleton is silicon-based than calcium-based, including bones and enamels. Colors of furs are black, white, gray, brown. Ahmuivns’ sexual organs have same location with humans, produce excreta are brown feces and blue urines same as humans.<br/>Society<br/>Ahmuivn race is militarism, xenophobia, authoritarianism. Patriarchal and traditional society operated under fascist dictatorship, aesthetics mix of Warhammer 40k and Star Wars, blend resemblance of Nazi Germany and Soviet Union. Frenyan religion is dominant in Frenyan Empire, Frenyan priests resembles priests from Warhammer 40k. Surveillance and propaganda.<br/>Frenyan Empire<br/>Frenyan Empire, fascist empire ruled by dictator Isok Khamsich, a capital of Frenyan Empire. Mix of Russian Empire and Nazi Germany, Imperium of Man from Warhammer 40k, Galactic Empire from Star Wars. Isokism is fascist ideology, symbol shape is Juche in left-sided direction and color is blue associated with color of ahmuivn bloods. Racial purity, ahmuivns are superior to humans and other extraterrestrials. Frenyan Empire committed genocides of extraterrestrials, utilizes exterminatus technique from Warhammer 40k to destroy alien homeworlds. Frenyan Empire poses barbaric threat to peace of intergalactic community.<br/>Religion<br/>Ahmuivn named Christ of Frenvek, he founded catholic Frenyan religion resembles Christianity, crucified in equator of Frenya, for our lord of ahmuivns. Frenyan bible forbids astrology, nudities, adulteries, fornications, blasphemies. Pornography, degeneracy, masturbation are violation of religion. Color red is prohibited in religion because it’s associated with sexuality. Marriage is between one husband and one wife.<br/>Military<br/>Military and soldiers are stormtroopers and space marines. Weapons are lightsabers and laser guns. Military vehicles are spaceships and space tanks. Military uniforms are painted with blue, depends color of plants, to camouflage. Frenyan Empire targeted enemies, including heretics, blasphemers, humans, extraterrestrial scum, traitors, witches, and mutants.</div><br/><br/>LLM response:<br/><div style="
