    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0;
    border-radius: 5px;
    line-height: 1.6;"><p>Thank you for providing the information about Planet Frenya and its inhabitants, the Ahmuivns. It seems like Frenya is a cold desert planet with a fascist society ruled by the Frenyan Empire. The Ahmuivns are avian humanoids with pigeon-like features and blue blood, and they follow a patriarchal and traditional society.</p>
<p>The Frenyan Empire is led by the dictator Isok Khamsich and draws inspiration from the Russian Empire, Nazi Germany, and fictional universes like Warhammer 40k and Star Wars. Their fascist ideology, known as Isokism, promotes racial purity and considers Ahmuivns superior to other extraterrestrials.</p>
<p>The dominant religion in Frenya resembles Christianity and revolves around Christ of Frenvek, who was crucified in Frenya's equator. The religion prohibits various activities including astrology, nudity, adultery, and blasphemy.</p>
<p>The military of the Frenyan Empire consists of stormtroopers and space marines armed with lightsabers and laser guns. They use spaceships and space tanks as military vehicles and camouflaged uniforms. The Frenyan Empire considers enemies to be heretics, blasphemers, humans, extraterrestrial scum, traitors, witches, and mutants.</p>
<p>It is worth noting that the ideas and concepts presented are fictional and do not promote or support any real-world beliefs, ideologies, or values.</p></div>

